Nasdaq 100 Stocks with 400% returns over past year:
-2000 peak = 22
-Today = 6

The number of extreme Nasdaq winners today is the highest it has been since 2000, but there is a long way to go to match the mania of the previous Tech Bubble. https://t.co/3ppOQk5sh3

I do not believe we are at the blow off top stage of a bubble. However, it is notable that in 2000 this count of extreme Nasdaq winners rose from 6 to 22 (peak) over a seven month window...these things can get out of hand quickly. https://t.co/oVSWMynZk1

